    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1046400/extras/bcc39d2ded436b3f2b9f5f14f0c9255b.poster.avif?t=1744187233\" width=620 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1046400/extras/bcc39d2ded436b3f2b9f5f14f0c9255b.webm?t=1744187233\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1046400/extras/bcc39d2ded436b3f2b9f5f14f0c9255b.mp4?t=1744187233\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>三名英勇的探险家在劫后的沙漠里游走，誓要把村子从绝望中救出来。他们很快找到一座黑暗扭曲的塔，塔身从星球深处冒出来，似乎隐藏了掌控他们生存的秘密。为了确保胜利，其中一人与死亡之提坦-厄毗米修斯签订了秘密协议。他们将可以无限重生，直到完成任务。探险家和他们的村庄将面临怎样的命运？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1046400/extras/0d023d5ba7e01971bf6ea7f8204dff6f.poster.avif?t=1744187233\" width=620 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1046400/extras/0d023d5ba7e01971bf6ea7f8204dff6f.webm?t=1744187233\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1046400/extras/0d023d5ba7e01971bf6ea7f8204dff6f.mp4?t=1744187233\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >「死亡只是开始」</h2>阿斯达伦：地球之泪是一款动作平台游戏，以残酷的垂死世界为背景，死亡成为了胜利的垫脚石！利用战士阿里亚斯、盗匪奎利和巫师阿尔格斯的技能和武器，您将登上神秘的高塔，寻找他们生存的答案。消灭可怕的怪物、寻找强大的道具、解决棘手的谜题，在提坦巨人的帮助下，您将通过重重考验到达塔顶。展开一个关于友谊和牺牲的故事，鼓起勇气，打倒巨人，保护弱小吧！勇敢拥抱死亡，让你的队友变强，改写他们的命运。隐藏在蛇塔的秘密，等待您一一揭开！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1046400/extras/7e2d9c5ae1cb610360b4db71e24e2b1e.poster.avif?t=1744187233\" width=620 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1046400/extras/7e2d9c5ae1cb610360b4db71e24e2b1e.webm?t=1744187233\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1046400/extras/7e2d9c5ae1cb610360b4db71e24e2b1e.mp4?t=1744187233\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>在黑暗奇幻的世界里，通过精致真实的像素艺术再现8元位动作冒险的辉煌岁月！您将在紧密相联的地下迷宫展开探索，享受高速紧凑的闯关体验。<br></li><li>游戏角色由世界著名漫画《半龙少女》作家见田龙介亲手设计！<br></li><li>以您喜欢的速度进行游戏—您可以在塔里仔细探索，逐渐培养角色的力量，或使用冒险的方法迅速攻上塔顶！<br></li><li>随意变更您的英雄，善用战士、弓箭手和巫师的独特技能挑战各个关卡。<br></li><li>与各式各样的敌人、巨型怪物和头目进行战斗！选择合适的英雄，找出怪物的弱点并消灭牠们！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1046400/extras/04057fd1a5843391576a03e615d1ec8a.poster.avif?t=1744187233\" width=620 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1046400/extras/04057fd1a5843391576a03e615d1ec8a.webm?t=1744187233\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1046400/extras/04057fd1a5843391576a03e615d1ec8a.mp4?t=1744187233\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>与死亡之提坦-厄毗米修斯进行交易，让角色变得更强大，改写他们的命运。<br></li><li>通过收集「镜子之剑」等各种强大的道具，赋予角色新的技能，开拓更多可能性。<br></li><li>善用营火保存游戏进度，更换角色和了解他们的过去。<br></li><li>多达数百个房间等待您去发掘——长时间的高难度探索，加上大量的关卡和秘密，好奇心旺盛的玩家非挑战不可！<br></li><li>感受由Matt Kap创作的扣人心弦的配乐-合共30多首原创芯片音乐！</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1046400/extras/ce244f8b9cb6bdbbbcfad82d86d30679.poster.avif?t=1744187233\" width=620 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1046400/extras/ce244f8b9cb6bdbbbcfad82d86d30679.webm?t=1744187233\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1046400/extras/ce244